‚Ä¢	Build hybrid deployment scripts (Docker + Kubernetes for private cloud/on-prem clients).
‚Ä¢	Claude assists in optimizing query performance, adding caching layer, writing multi-region replication logic.
Deliverable: Enterprise-ready multi-tenant, multi-branch, AI-driven platform supporting 1,000+ users across regions.
 
